data.description: Can you see the Forest for the Trees? It's Easy!  This could be your blank Canvas!  Rood, Water Heater & the rest is simple Cosmetic! There's No Reason you can't take occupancy Now! Everything works perfectly!  Sure, she's got Blemishes... but these can be fixed as you go ~ It's a 2005 Craftsman built ~ Below market value @ $145. per sq ft ~ ALL major components are in GREAT OPERATIONAL ORDER & currently functioning as intended! This 1324 sf feels like a 1550 sf due to open Floor plan & Vaulted Ceilings.  Bring this baby back to her Gorgeous Self! If you can See the Forest for the Trees, you're 90% of the way there! This property offers  a) Brick Home on all 4 Sides b) Flat topography of HALF ACRE Parcel  c) No HOA telling you what to do! Split Floor plan, all Electric & Tile Flooring in Main Areas.  'AS-IS'.  Seller will provide a 1 year Home Warranty to promote optimism! Double Gate entry to Backyard provides ample room for Boat, Camper, Tractor etc.  Property Line extends beyond back fence line.  See you Soon!
